chapters.title: If You Multiply the Opposite Sides and Add Up those Products You Will Get the Product of the Two Diagonals
The Product of the Opposite Sides
How Can You Catch all Lions in Africa
Ptolemies Theorem Reveals a Link between Pentagon's and the Golden Ratio
